  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, NameTag, DynamicSimuEvent, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class DynamicSimuEventImpl
extends NameTagImpl
implements DynamicSimuEvent
    An implementation of the model object 'Dynamic Event'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Start Time Sec
    • Duration Sec
    • Type
    • Permanent
    • Branch Fault
    • Branch Dynamic Event
    • Bus Fault
    • Bus Dynamic Event
    • Bus Device Dynamic Event
